snippet.title: Ballads of Hongye - Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Ballads of Hongye is a unique city-builder strategy game. As the local magistrate, you must carefully plan and act to complete the various challenges in different environments to earn the right to rule the lands. Build a thriving city and revive Hongye County as you discover a unique story. The game will be available on November 30th.
